Visualization for green-dash.
=============================

See https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=vJGdxnaq9_0 for a video.

Installation
------------
Prerequisites:
- node.js
- npm

- kafka with the following live topics: standardized-by-tag-topic, normalized-by-tag-topic, grouped-by-tag-topic, deviation-topic
  These topics are populated by green-dash/stream-processor.
- a running instance of green-dash/data-player

Before running for the first time execute:
    npm install

Configuration
-------------
Some configuration settings can be made in the file
    conf/application.json

Running
-------
Execute:

    node server.js

And point your browser to
    http://localhost:3010/kitchensink.html


